Class OptimisticConcurrentStack<E>

java.lang.Object

Type Parameters:

All Implemented Interfaces:
ConcurrentStack<E>
public final class OptimisticConcurrentStack<E>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ConcurrentStack<E>

A concurrent stack using Treiber's algorithm. This is very efficient for low concurrency levels, but becomes slow when thrashed.
